Pump Control Feature Branch
The control is installed with a Pump, Relay, ESP32


 What This Branch Implements

This branch is responsible for pump/valve control and automatic dispensing management in the Flow Sensor Dispensing System.

Implemented Features:
- ✅ Control of relay/pump on - GPIO 26
- ✅ Automatic - start and stop of the pump based on system state
- ✅ Auto-stop functionality when target volume reaches ≥ 850 ml
- ✅ Integration between button input and pump output
- ✅ Safe pump state management (ON/OFF)
- ✅ Real-time synchronization with flow sensor readings
- ✅ Prevention of overflow by stopping at the required 850 ml target

Control added feature, added pump pin configuration, relay control logic, and auto-stop at 850 m


 Pump Behavior

- when dispensing = true: Pump/relay turns ON (HIGH)
- when dispensing = false: Pump/relay turns OFF (LOW)
- Automatic shutdown: Pump stops automatically when `totalVolume_ml >= 850`
- LCD feedback: Shows "Dispensing..." or "Target Reached! 850 ml Done"
